HEADWORD: Stabling
<hw>Sta"bling</hw> <pr>(-bl⟦icr⟧ng)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The act or practice of keeping horses and cattle in a
stable.</def>⟦br⟧
